    <h3>Refunds</h3>
    <p>We are not in the business of stealing deposits. We are in the business of renting apartments!</p>
    <p>On case-by-case occasions, our policy is to talk to the tenants if the landlord occurred a loss as a result of the tenants backing out of signing a lease. We work towards resolution for both parties involved. Most commonly we will ask the clients to forfeit part of their deposit and if we find replacement tenants to meet the same lease terms we refund everything.</p>
    <p>Rejected deposits will be returned only by company check at the Bushwick office. Please give administration 24 hours notice for a refund check.</p>
    <h3>Flip’em</h3>
